 2021-06062021-06-17,  ,  ,  PSPC,  NCC, 
ActNational Capital Act
SubjectAcquisition of Property and lease with York Realty Inc. ** NCC **
PrecisOrder approving (1) the acquisition by the National Capital Commission from the City of Ottawa of the real property located near the intersection of Walkley Road and Russell Road, in Ottawa, Ontario; and (2) that the National Capital Commission enter a lease with York Realty Inc. for a period of 99 years, for real property located at 2391 Walkley Road and 2646 Walkley Road, in Ottawa, Ontario.
